{"tid":1471302,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"消費力道減 7月支那零售數據下滑 遠差預期","createTime":"2019-08-14T08:38:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T09:10:59.000Z","uid":32511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"70f0551279a2c1280bba62c5ac03906bad0691e0","tid":1471302,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:38:35.000Z","msg":"中國統計局今 (14) 日公布 7 月份，中國消費品零售總額達人民幣 3.3 兆元，名目年增率 7.6%，預期 8.4%，前期為 9.8%。若扣除汽車，消費品零售額達人民幣 3 兆元，年增 8.8%。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/4367101/l/f143fdb4b5e2f8c673eee527fbce830c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F4367101%2Fl%2Ff143fdb4b5e2f8c673eee527fbce830c.jpg&h=a36e2f32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1～7 月，中國消費品零售總額人民幣 22.8 兆元，年增 8.3%。若扣除汽車，消費品零售額達人民幣 20.6 兆元，年增 9.2%。<br />\n<br />\n依經營單位所在地分，7 月，城鎮消費品零售額人民幣 2.84 兆元，年增 7.4%；鄉村消費品零售額人民幣 4719 億元，年增 8.6%。<br />\n<br />\n1～7 月，城鎮消費品零售額人民幣 19.5 兆元，年增 8.2%；鄉村消費品零售額人民幣 3.3 兆元，年增 9%。<br />\n<br />\n1～7 月，中國網路零售額人民幣 5.6 兆元，年增 16.8%，漲幅比 1～6 月下滑 1 個百分點。其中，實物商品網路零售額人民幣 4.4 兆元，年增 20.9%，佔整體消費品零售總額比重達 19.4%，比去年同期提升 2.1 個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n業內指出，6 月份零售總額年增逼近雙位數，創下今年以來單月新高，主要是受到「國五標準」車型去庫存帶動汽車銷售超出預期。<br />\n<br />\n進入 7 月後，汽車「國六標準」上路，使得汽車銷售成長動能相對減弱不少，這也導致 7 月份零售銷售下滑幅度較高的主因。<br />\n<br />\n業內人士表示，中國就業情況相對平穩，所以消費再大幅下滑的風險有限。隨著減稅降費持續深化，變相提升民眾收入，這也利於刺激消費。不過，美中貿易所帶來的不確定性，對於消費會產生一定的影響性。<br />\n<br />\n中國申萬宏源指出，4 月 1 日增值稅結構性減稅落地，降價效應不斷向高階消費品，如家電、大中型消費電子產品等擴散，預計家電、化妝品、通訊設備等高階消費品的消費成長速度能保持偏高幅度，支持整體消費市場發展。"},{"pid":"e2f4cbc4aeee19ab5e33bbee61ee880da4c9e2fb","tid":1471302,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:39:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg&h=b7bac505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg&h=42f5c084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png&h=4a3dc024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg&h=42d70b2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a1d08bb10111de8c7baa8b42acdb80f52cc2aa4","tid":1471302,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:10:59.000Z","msg":"除左恭喜都唔知講咩好"}]}